-align: -0.671ex; width:3.483ex; height:2.343ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle +_{=
m}}"></span> and <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><=
span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display=
: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\di=
splaystyle \cdot _{m}}">
